    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Process invented in the late 20th century by Jon Cone, where special, monochromatic inks are used in conjunction with software to produce black and white inkjet prints using consumer printers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047422/Piezography (R) [online] (2005-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Proceso inventado en el siglo XX por Jon Cone, donde las tintas monocromáticas se utilizan conjuntamente con software (PC) para producir impresiones blancas y negras, por medio de la inyección de tintas usando las impresoras comunes. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Procedé dat aan het eind van de 20ste eeuw is bedacht door Jon Cone, waarbij speciale monochromatische inkten met software worden gecombineerd om inkjetafdrukken in zwart-wit te maken met consumentenprinters.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>二十世紀晚期由瓊‧科恩(Jon Cone)所發明的印刷技法，將一種特殊單色墨水和電腦軟體結合運用，透過一般印表機印製出黑白噴墨印刷品。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
